
### Blog Management System ###
A simple, elegant, and modern Blog Posting Platform built with Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, and Pug.
It allows users to create, edit, search, and manage blog posts with authentication and admin control features.


# Functions
User registration and login
- Register and login as blog posting users
- View blog posts posted by other users
- Create, view, edit, delete your own blog posts
- Search blog posts by title or tags
- Admin panel to manage blog posts and users

# Features
- Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Modern UI with Bootstrap 5 styling
- Flash messages for user feedback
- Secure authentication and CSRF protection
- Reusable components
- Clean and maintainable code structure

# Technology stack
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- Database: MongoDB with Mongoose
- Templating Engine: Pug
- Styling: Bootstrap 5, Custom CSS
- Authentication: Passport.js (Local Strategy)
- Validation: Joi
- Security: CSRF Protection
- Other: Method-Override (for PUT and DELETE)


